sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Agent as OpenClaw Agent
    participant SC as Skill Catalog
    participant FS as Filesystem
    participant Skill as Skill Folder
    participant Proc as External Process

    User->>Agent: Request (e.g., "Build snake game")
    Agent->>SC: findMatchingSkill(request)
    SC->>SC: search SKILL.md frontmatter (name, description)
    SC-->>Agent: coding-agent
    Agent->>Skill: read SKILL.md
    Skill-->>Agent: documentation content
    Agent->>Agent: parse requirements (anyBins: ["claude","codex","pi"])
    Agent->>FS: which("codex")? (check binary)
    FS-->>Agent: "/usr/local/bin/codex"
    Agent->>Agent: construct command:<br/>bash pty:true workdir:/tmp/snake command:"codex --full-auto exec 'Build a snake game...'"
    Agent->>Proc: spawn(bash, args)
    Proc->>Proc: run codex
    Proc-->>Agent: stdout/stderr stream
    Agent->>Agent: monitor via process:log, poll
    Proc-->>Agent: exit(code=0)
    Agent-->>User: result (snake game built)